nexigon — metadata-only Debian source package
==============================================

This source package exists to satisfy archives and image builders that
require a source package to accompany every binary package. It is not
buildable.

The shipped nexigon-agent-* and nexigon-cli-* binaries are
cross-compiled by the upstream release pipeline; see
.github/workflows/pipeline.yml and scripts/build-debs.sh in the
upstream repository for the actual build process.

The exact upstream commit that produced the binaries is recorded in
the GIT_COMMIT file at the top of this source package. The Cargo.lock
file captures the resolved Rust dependency graph at that commit.

Upstream source: https://github.com/nexigon/nexigon/
